  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437680/extras/bb32e213283ce61f00dadcd5739391cd.avif?t=1773950012\" alt=\"\"width=1536 height=550 /></span>**Knight Pistachio** is a 2D action platformer inspired by classic 90s games. Play as Pistachio, the mysterious knight who must defeat Akurg, the leader who ruined his vacation and came to control all the planets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ Make your way across diverse planets, confronting enemies and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Classic side-scrolling gameplay with modern controls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Diverse levels that don't focus on just one type of gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unique boss battles that require focus and reflexes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Stunning graphics and sound effects that replace the music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Explore planets with challenging levels and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Estimated Playtime: 2 to 4 hours, depending on your skill.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437680/extras/bb32e213283ce61f00dadcd5739391cd.avif?t=1773950012\" alt=\"\"width=1536 height=550 /></span>**Knight Pistachio** is a 2D action platformer inspired by classic 90s games. Play as Pistachio, the mysterious knight who must defeat Akurg, the leader who ruined his vacation and came to control all the planets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ Make your way across diverse planets, confronting enemies and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Classic side-scrolling gameplay with modern controls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Diverse levels that don't focus on just one type of gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unique boss battles that require focus and reflexes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Stunning graphics and sound effects that replace the music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Explore planets with challenging levels and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Estimated Playtime: 2 to 4 hours, depending on your skill.</p>",
